Interface ExtensionMethods

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HtmlExtensionMethods

    public interface ExtensionMethods
    Extension methods marker interface. Extension methods are created by implementing this interface and creating static methods in the class with at lease one parameter. The first parameter of each extension method determines the class that the method extends.
